<div class='main-instructions'>
  <span class='loud'>
      You've made <%= @total_count %> changes
  </span>
  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-7'>
      <h2>Instructions:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Most of what you see on this page CAN be changed!</li>
        <li>
          Individual components (like the 'Youi' text in the top-left corner of the page) are changeable if they have a  <span class='green'>green</span> border when you <strong>hover over them</strong>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Sections such as the footer can be changed using the <strong>set of buttons below</strong>.
        </li>
        <li>
          Click the <strong>'Edit Mode'</strong> button to the right to turn off the hover interactions so you can see your <em>beautiful</em> site!
        </li>
        <li>
          Click the <strong>'Generate CSS'</strong> button to view the styles for the current website.
        </li>
        <li>
          To learn more, please scroll below and read the "About" section.
        </li>
        <li>Oh, and don't forget to read the directions!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class='col-md-5'>
      <div class='edit-container'>
        <button class="edit button-selector-2 button-selector-<%= @button_selector_id_2%>">Edit Mode</button>
        <span class="edit-mode">On</span>
         <button class='button-selector-2 button-selector-<%= @button_selector_id_2%>' data-toggle="modal" data-target="#current-CSS">
            Current CSS
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>